name: Macrobenthos of the Voordelta (Grevelingen, Oosterschelde) in 1988 and 1989
description: Counts of bivalves and polychaetes per family forseveralreplicates sampled at 4 stations in the Voordelta between April 1988 and March1989 and average density and biomassof macrobenthos species for several clustered stations sampled in the Grevelingen andOosterschelde area between July and August 1988. The data were digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Craeymeersch, J.A.; Buijs, J.; Brand, R.; Hannewijk, A.; Sistermans,W.C.H.; Stikvoort, E. (1990). Benthosonderzoek in relatie tot abiotischedynamiek het macrobenthos van de Voordelta: interimrapportagejuli 1989. DIHO rapporten en verslagen, 1990(4). Dienst HydrologischOnderzoek (DIHO): Yerseke. 72 pp.
